        <abstract> 
<p>Comments on W. H. Harvey’s article on a monstrous <hi rend="italic">Begonia</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Gard. Chron.</hi> 18 Feb 1860].</p> 
            <p>Is astonished at being attacked for not allowing great and abrupt variations under nature. More evidence needed to make CD admit that forms have often changed "by saltum".</p>
